---
title: Barre de progression
active: {
    components: {
        progress-bar: true
    }
}
root: ../
progressBars: ['0',  '20', '40',  '60',  '80',  '100']
---
{{#extend "menu-page"}}
{{#content "content"}}
{{#> components-title desc="Barres de progression"}}{{/components-title }}

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-normal-1" title="Barre de progression fine" do="true"}}

        {{#content "light"}}
            <progress class="progress is-small is-info" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-small is-success" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-small is-warning" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-small is-danger" value="40" max="100">%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-small is-primary" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "do"}}
            <p>La barre de progression fine s'utilise en ajoutant la classe <strong class="has-text-primary">.small</strong></p>
            <p>Elle peut servir dans les formulaires par exemple, en dessous du champs mot de passe, pour déterminer la force de celui-ci.</p>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-normal-1" title="Barre de progression droite"}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <progress class="progress is-info" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-success" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-warning" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-danger" value="40" max="100">%</progress>
            <progress class="progress is-primary" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-normal-2" title="Barre de progression empilée"}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <div class="progress is-stacked">
                <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" style="width: 15%" aria-valuenow="15" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                <div class="progress-bar is-success" role="progressbar" style="width: 30%" aria-valuenow="30" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
                <div class="progress-bar is-warning" role="progressbar" style="width: 20%" aria-valuenow="20" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
            </div>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-normal-3" title="Barre de progression avec légende unique"}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <progress class="progress is-info" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <p class="has-text-centered text is-2">illimité</p>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-normal-4" title="Barre de progression avec légende aux extrémités"}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <progress class="progress is-info" value="15" max="100">15%</progress>
            <div class="columns is-mobile">
                <div class="column">
                    <p class="text is-2">0 Go</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-narrow">
                    <p class="text is-2">5 Go</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

<section class="section">
    {{#> snippet id="progress-circle" do="true" warning="true" title="Barre de progression circulaire"}}
        {{#content "light"}}
            <div class="progress-circle-group">
                <div class="progress-circle" style="--secondary: 0; --tertiary: 1; --warning: 0; --empty: 0">
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-secondary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-tertiary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-warning"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-empty"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-content">
                        <div class="progress-circle-title">XX Go</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="progress-circle" style="--secondary: 0.25; --tertiary: 0.25; --warning: 0; --empty: 0.5">
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-secondary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-tertiary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-warning"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-empty"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-content">
                        <div class="progress-circle-title">XX Go</div>
                        <div class="progress-circle-sub">Texte lorem</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="progress-circle" style="--secondary: 0; --tertiary: 0.25; --warning: 0.5; --empty: 0.25">
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-secondary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-tertiary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-warning"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-empty"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-content">
                        <div class="progress-circle-title">XX Go</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="progress-circle" style="--secondary: 0; --tertiary: 0; --warning: 1; --empty: 0">
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-secondary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-tertiary"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-warning"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-slice progress-circle-background-empty"></div>
                    <div class="progress-circle-content">
                        <div class="progress-circle-title has-text-warning">XX Go</div>
                        <div class="progress-circle-sub has-text-warning">Texte lorem</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "do"}}
            <p>1/ La barre de progression circulaire, se compose de 4 couleurs possibles :</p>
            <ul class="list">
                <li><strong>progress-circle-background-secondary</strong></li>
                <li><strong>progress-circle-background-tertiary</strong></li>
                <li><strong>progress-circle-background-warning</strong></li>
                <br>
                <li>Quand une partie de la <em>progress-circle</em> est vide alors on lui ajoute la classe : <br>
                    <strong>progress-circle-background-empty</strong>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <p>2/ Les pourcentages se décident dans la propriété <em>style=""</em> de la classe <br> <strong class="has-text-primary">.progress-circle</strong>. Le total de chaque couleur devra faire <strong>100%</strong>.</p>
            <p class="is-italic">
                <u>Exemple ci-dessus (ayant un total de 100%):</u> <br>
                <ul>
                    <li>--secondary: 0 (représente 0%)</li>
                    <li>--tertiary: 0.25 (représente 25%)</li>
                    <li>--warning: 0.5 (représente 50%)</li>
                    <li>--empty: 0.25 (représente 25%)</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <br>
        {{/content}}

        {{#content "warning"}}
            <p>Si on souhaite mettre seulement 2 couleurs, il va falloir quand même les indiquer avec la valeur 0.</p>
            <p>La valeur de la couleur "grise" devra être le restant pour avoir un total de 100%.</p>
        {{/content}}
    {{/snippet}}
</section>

{{/content}}
{{/extend}}
